Note:
Runa Standard Library: Blockchain Wallets Module

Provides comprehensive cryptocurrency wallet management and operations for multiple
blockchain networks. Implements enterprise-grade wallet functionality including
HD wallet generation, multi-signature support, hardware wallet integration, and
secure key management. Competitive with production wallet implementations in
MetaMask, Trust Wallet, Ledger Live, and other leading wallet solutions.

Features:
- Hierarchical Deterministic (HD) wallet generation with BIP32/39/44 support
- Multi-signature wallet creation and transaction coordination
- Hardware wallet integration (Ledger, Trezor, KeepKey)
- Hot and cold wallet management with security controls
- Multi-chain wallet support (Bitcoin, Ethereum, and 50+ networks)
- Advanced key derivation and address generation
- Transaction signing with multiple signature schemes
- Wallet recovery and backup management with seed phrases
- Address book and contact management
- Portfolio tracking and balance aggregation across chains
- DeFi integration with automated yield farming and staking
- NFT collection management and marketplace integration
- Cross-chain asset management and bridge coordination
- Security features including biometric authentication and MFA
- Institutional-grade custody and compliance integration
:End Note

Note: Core Wallet Types
